<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06151i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06151i">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06151i"> 151(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Walk in the same</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">&ldquo;WHAT DID YOUR GODFATHERS AND GODMOTHERS THEN FOR YOU?&rdquo; <br>&ldquo;THEY DID PROMISE AND VOW THREE THINGS IN MY NAME. FIRST, THAT I SHOULD RENOUNCE THE DEVIL AND ALL HIS WORKS, THE POMPS AND VANITY OF THIS WICKED WORLD, AND ALL THE SINFUL LUSTS OF THE FLESH. SECONDLY, THAT I SHOULD BELIEVE ALL THE ARTICLES OF THE CHRISTIAN FAITH. AND, THIRDLY, THAT I SHOULD KEEP GOD&apos;S HOLY WILL AND COMMANDMENTS, AND <mark>WALK IN THE SAME</mark> ALL THE DAYS OF MY LIFE. <small> Anonymous, <a name="ATCC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ATCC"><cite title="source">Analysis of the Church Catechism</cite></a> (1879) 10</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
